messages.content: What nodes are available in the ComfyUI-Fans extension?
The ComfyUI-Fans extension contains 4 KÃ¼n 4 viciss nodes: Fans Styler, Fans Text Concat, Fans Prompt Styler Postive, and Fans Prompt Styler Negative.
How do I install the ComfyUI-Fans extension?
Clone the repository to your ComfyUI `custom_nodes` directory and restart your ComfyUI.
What are the guidelines and restrictions for using the ComfyUI-Fans extension?
The documentation outlines specific rules regarding CSV filenames, content editing, output format, integration with other plugins, and screenshot usage.
